<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97405557726078></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97405557726078><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=7&mid=97405557726078>RE: Low-Mid 30s hunting/soloing?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Nov 12th 1:59 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>For the low 30s cleric, a great place to solo is the Lake of Ill Omen. Find yourself a spot on the shores of the lake near the Sarnak fortress and cast Sense Undead. You should be able to pick up the presence of a Charbone, Warbone, or Icebone Skeleton. Pull to the lake shore to get out of the way of the roaming mobs.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
