	   <tr><td colspan=2>In the beginnig you should summon your magical hammer, and buy a round shield (AC 5 or AC 6)<br><br>Around lvl 10, you should be able to loot a Bronze 1HB hammer or mace, buy a AC 8 shield (cannot remmeber the name)<br><br>At lvl 20, you should be able to afford a Fine steel hammer or mace (ask a highlevel, they usually give them away). Else buy it, for around 5 pp.<br><br>Also at lvl 20 you should consider getting a Shiny Brass Shield. Its easily obtained, search for the shield on this site, and youll learn how to obtain it.<br><br>At lvl 30 Ill suggest you get a Black Enamelled mace and a crested mistmoore shield. They are pretty hard to get, but defends you well, and enables you to do around 20 dmg pr hit. Just to finish off nearly dead foes, and dispose off trash that jumps you.<br><br>At lvl 40 Ill suppose you submit a new note here. You will then be more confortable with the game, and be better of making your own discisions...<br><br>Good luck. Just ask other players or inspect them, ask for their lvl, and note what weapon and shield they are using.<br><br>I cannot recommnd a 2HB weapon for you fellow cleric, youll loose the AC and enchantments of the shield.<br><br>You wont melee later after lvl 25 or so, therefore 2HB's extra damage wont be any good.<br><br>Dark greetings<br><br>Sangreal Soulburner<br>Cazic-Thule<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
