	   <tr><td colspan=2>First off, I agree with Sangreal's message on not buying/using 2hb as you will pretty much leave that skill to waste later on.  As to the lvls and weapons suggested by Sangreal I'd pretty much agree, except that you will probably get those items much sooner.  <br>Around lvl 5, if you are completely new and start with 0 cash, you should try to have a cracked staff by lvl 2, and a bronze, store bought or looted by lvl 5-6.  At lvl 10, you can either use the summoned hammer, if it's better than a FS weapon which you should already have.  At lvl 20, you should have at least advanced to a Screaming mace, CIMS, or possibly a Enameled black mace, which are good 1hb's for their lvl.<br>Around lvl 30, you should have gotten a group together to help you get some of the Solusek Ro, armor which would include the Cadeceus of Sacrement, or saved and scraped up enough money to buy another good weapon like a Enchanted FS, Sharkbone warhammer, Wraithbone hammer, etc.  These weapons still serve as good through lvl 40, unless you can find or loot something better.  At lvl 50 and high 40's you could probably go for a new Kunark weapon like a Ringed Mace of the Ykesha, or a Solusek Efreeti Warhammer etc.<br>Gedran<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
