<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=96819175130910></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96819175130910><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=7&mid=96819175130910>Soloing DE Cleric - killing more then undead</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
